<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 20:08:36 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列被哈马斯扣为人质的照片荣获著名奖项，但招致批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/photo-of-israeli-being-taken-hostage-by-hamas-wins-renowned-award-drawing-criticism/0000018e-861c-d9dd-a39f-cefe1eb40000</link><description>批评者表示，选择沙尼·卢克（Shani Louk）被驱车进入加沙的照片是不合适的，而她的父亲则表示这张照片是历史的一部分。</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/photo-of-israeli-being-taken-hostage-by-hamas-wins-renowned-award-drawing-criticism/0000018e-861c-d9dd-a39f-cefe1eb40000</guid></item><item><title>巴西博尔索纳罗请求法院允许接受内塔尼亚胡访问以色列的邀请</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/brazils-bolsonaro-requests-court-permission-to-accept-netanyahus-invite-to-israel/0000018e-865d-d49b-a3bf-f65f38530000</link><description>名誉扫地的巴西前领导人雅伊尔·博尔索纳罗正在寻求巴西当局的许可，归还被扣押的护照，以便他能够访问以色列。巴西联邦警察在调查他是否试图在 2023 年发动起义以继续掌权时没收了他的护照</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:32:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/brazils-bolsonaro-requests-court-permission-to-accept-netanyahus-invite-to-israel/0000018e-865d-d49b-a3bf-f65f38530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列颁奖仪式将在斯德洛特而不是耶路撒冷举行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-ceremony-to-be-held-in-sderot-instead-of-jerusalem/0000018e-8653-d641-abee-cff7d9bb0000</link><description>教育部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来的首次颁奖典礼将在南部城市举行，并公布了获奖者的完整名单，其中包括企业家和民主活动人士埃亚尔·沃尔德曼 (Eyal Waldman)</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 19:30:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-prize-ceremony-to-be-held-in-sderot-instead-of-jerusalem/0000018e-8653-d641-abee-cff7d9bb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 首次赢得耶什·阿蒂德 (Yesh Atid) 党初选</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-opposition-leader-yair-lapid-wins-first-ever-yesh-atid-party-primary/0000018e-8632-d9dd-a39f-cef251390000</link><description>前总理、现任反对党领袖拉皮德赢得了 52.5% 的选票，以 29 票击败挑战者拉姆·本·巴拉克（拉皮德 308 票，本·巴拉克 279 票）。结果比预期的要窄，一些人指责选民自满地认为拉皮德会获胜</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 18:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/israeli-opposition-leader-yair-lapid-wins-first-ever-yesh-atid-party-primary/0000018e-8632-d9dd-a39f-cef251390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 174 天：巴勒斯坦总理穆斯塔法组建新政府</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-174-palestinian-pm-mustafa-forms-new-government/0000018e-8609-d49b-a3bf-f61fcbcf0000</link><description>以色列国家安全委员会发布旅行警告，请勿前往土耳其、摩洛哥、埃及和约旦 ■ 以色列国防军表示，巴勒斯坦伊斯兰圣战恐怖分子承认他于 10 月 7 日强奸了以色列妇女 ■ 国际法院命令以色列采取措施，确保食品畅通无阻地进入加沙 ■ 巴勒斯坦穆斯塔法总理组建新政府 ■ 美国和以色列正在努力确定以色列代表团访问的新日期 ■ 战争结束 174 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 17:27:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-174-palestinian-pm-mustafa-forms-new-government/0000018e-8609-d49b-a3bf-f61fcbcf0000</guid></item><item><title>下令非法搜查巴勒斯坦妇女生殖器的以色列官员获得晋升</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officer-who-ordered-illegal-search-of-palestinian-womans-genitals-gets-promotion/0000018e-85bf-d9b3-abcf-87ff99520000</link><description>尽管指挥官对审讯人员的陈述与进行搜查的士兵的说法相矛盾，但对该事件的调查已于三年前终止</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officer-who-ordered-illegal-search-of-palestinian-womans-genitals-gets-promotion/0000018e-85bf-d9b3-abcf-87ff99520000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇和雷格夫部长在埃拉特房地产会议上在台下发出嘘声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/ministers-smotrich-and-regev-booed-off-stage-at-eilat-real-estate-conference/0000018e-8586-df92-a5ff-e7aeb77f0000</link><description>在度假城市埃拉特举行的房地产会议上，财政部长贝扎莱尔·斯莫特里奇和交通部长米里·雷格夫在一片嘘声中离开了讲台。一位与会者想知道为什么选择两位部长作为发言人。 “与现实完全脱节，”他说</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/ministers-smotrich-and-regev-booed-off-stage-at-eilat-real-estate-conference/0000018e-8586-df92-a5ff-e7aeb77f0000</guid></item><item><title>国际法院命令以色列增加对加沙的人道主义援助，呼吁立即释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-28/ty-article/world-court-orders-israel-to-take-measures-to-ensure-food-gets-into-gaza/0000018e-85d9-d49b-a3bf-f5df73b40000</link><description>在南非请求世界法院采取额外措施后，国际法院命令以色列必须开放更多陆路过境点，以向加沙运送粮食和其他援助物资，“鉴于加沙人面临的生活条件不断恶化”，“特别是疫情蔓延”。饥荒和饥饿”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 16:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-28/ty-article/world-court-orders-israel-to-take-measures-to-ensure-food-gets-into-gaza/0000018e-85d9-d49b-a3bf-f5df73b40000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的全日制托拉学生比犹太历史上任何时候都多。这已经变得无法忍受</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</link><description>正是因为《托拉》研究对我来说如此珍贵，所以我想保留它，但要做到这一点，我们必须打破当今的范式，即成千上万的人在犹太学院学习，享受大量的国家福利，但不加入劳动力或以色列国防军。我们需要一个新模型</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:40:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-28/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-more-full-time-torah-students-than-ever-in-jewish-history-its-intolerable/0000018e-84bf-df27-adee-a6ff10df0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙的草莓丰收曾经是丰收的象征，现在却是战争的另一个受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</link><description>自 1967 年以来，加沙人就以收获“红色黄金”草莓而自豪，草莓在加沙地带被称为“红色黄金”。现在，加沙北部约 40% 的耕地变成废墟，农民对未来感到担忧</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 15:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/gazas-strawberry-harvest-once-a-symbol-of-abundance-is-another-victim-of-the-war/0000018e-857c-d0d3-a98e-d7ffc2940000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向穆斯林占多数的国家和欧洲电视网发出旅行警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</link><description>以色列国家安全委员会敦促以色列人避免前往土耳其、摩洛哥、埃及和约旦。它补充说，计划参加瑞典欧洲电视网或法国奥运会的以色列人应避免表现出“以色列”特征</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:57:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-issues-travel-warnings-to-muslim-countries-and-the-eurovision/0000018e-8572-d6fd-a78f-a77ffe700000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其的另一场选举意味着埃尔多安再次夺权</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/another-election-in-turkey-means-another-erdogan-power-grab/0000018e-84ec-df27-adee-a6fe60080000</link><description>在土耳其，每次举行选举，该国就离成为一个有意义的民主国家又迈出了一步。本周末的地方选举看起来将延续惨淡的模式</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/another-election-in-turkey-means-another-erdogan-power-grab/0000018e-84ec-df27-adee-a6fe60080000</guid></item><item><title>法国将对在加沙犯下战争罪的法以士兵采取法律行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/france-to-take-legal-action-against-french-israeli-soldiers-involved-in-war-crimes-in-gaza/0000018e-8530-d0d3-a98e-d7ff169e0000</link><description>在左翼政党的压力下，外交部表示将对任何在加沙从事构成战争罪活动的双重国籍士兵采取法律行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 14:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/france-to-take-legal-action-against-french-israeli-soldiers-involved-in-war-crimes-in-gaza/0000018e-8530-d0d3-a98e-d7ff169e0000</guid></item><item><title>她的兄弟活埋了她：巴勒斯坦-以色列导演敢于批评名誉杀人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-story-about-a-palestinian-woman-who-was-buried-alive-but-survived/0000018e-7fd3-d669-a9fe-7fff0cd10000</link><description>出生于拿撒勒的巴勒斯坦导演谢迪·斯鲁尔在以色列电视台播出其酝酿已久的电视剧《Fadia》时，讲述了他为何拒绝对社会中女性被谋杀的事件保持沉默</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-a-story-about-a-palestinian-woman-who-was-buried-alive-but-survived/0000018e-7fd3-d669-a9fe-7fff0cd10000</guid></item><item><title>这些以色列人在 10 月 7 日之前遭受过性虐待。现在他们再次受苦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-israelis-were-sexually-abused-before-oct-7-now-theyre-suffering-all-over-again/0000018e-7fa5-df6d-a7ef-ffe5539a0000</link><description>随着所有有关哈马斯遭受性暴力的新闻，过去遭受过性虐待的以色列人发现自己正在重温他们的创伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 12:15:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/these-israelis-were-sexually-abused-before-oct-7-now-theyre-suffering-all-over-again/0000018e-7fa5-df6d-a7ef-ffe5539a0000</guid></item><item><title>反内塔尼亚胡抗议者会见辛贝特，向他们通报针对总理的抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-protesters-meet-with-shin-ben-inform-them-about-protests-against-pm/0000018e-848f-d49b-a3bf-f49fcbec0000</link><description>这次会议被认为非常不寻常，其目的是在总理内塔尼亚胡私人住宅外每周举行的抗议活动中“防止跨越红线”，因为辛贝特官员担心，如果抗议者违反红线，可能会被总理的一名警卫开枪射杀。住宅的周长</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-protesters-meet-with-shin-ben-inform-them-about-protests-against-pm/0000018e-848f-d49b-a3bf-f49fcbec0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡破坏人质交易的机会，国防部长感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-is-sabotaging-chances-for-a-hostage-deal-and-defense-chiefs-are-angry/0000018e-8136-d0d3-a98e-d7ffa0f00000</link><description>据信，哈马斯在加沙扣押的人质中只有 60 至 70 人还活着，但谈判很复杂，并且因总理可疑的借口而陷入僵局</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 11:43:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-is-sabotaging-chances-for-a-hostage-deal-and-defense-chiefs-are-angry/0000018e-8136-d0d3-a98e-d7ffa0f00000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日被绑架的以色列士兵的父母指责内塔尼亚胡政府抛弃他们的儿子，要求与哈马斯达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</link><description>在与总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡会面之前，被哈马斯扣押的以色列士兵的父母声称，内塔尼亚胡“只是在六个月的许多官方请求和媒体请求后才与以色列士兵会面”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 10:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-soldiers-kidnapped-on-oct-7-accuse-netanyahu-govt-of-abandoning-their-sons/0000018e-8469-d0d3-a98e-d6ff230e0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学教授怀疑哈马斯10月7日性侵事件 澄清后将复职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</link><description>巴勒斯坦学者 Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian 教授于 10 月 7 日发表对哈马斯性侵犯程度表示怀疑的言论后，希伯来大学撤销了她的停职资格</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-prof-who-doubted-hamas-sexual-assaults-to-be-reinstated-after-recanting/0000018e-841b-da1d-a1bf-aefb01d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周五早上开始实行夏令时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</link><description>夏令时将于周五凌晨 2 点生效</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:29:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/daylight-saving-time-takes-effect-in-israel-friday-morning/0000018e-8458-d0d3-a98e-d6ff3a200000</guid></item></channel></rss>